    "format": "<style>\n/* common row */\n.cf-row{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; padding:6px 0; }\n.cf-label{ color: var(--cf-text); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }\n\n/* ON/OFF status pills */\n.cf-pill{ min-width:54px; text-align:center; padding:6px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing:.2px; }\n.cf-on{ background: rgba(40,167,69,.18); border:1px solid rgba(40,167,69,.45); color:#7CFF9C; }\n.cf-off{ background: rgba(220,53,69,.14); border:1px solid rgba(220,53,69,.45); color:#FF7C88; }\n\n/* dot lamps */\n.cf-dot{ width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:50%; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.12) inset; }\n.cf-dot-on{ background: rgba(40,167,69,1); box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(40,167,69,.55); }\n.cf-dot-off{ background: rgba(220,53,69,1); box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(220,53,69,.35); }\n</style>",
